reviews: I was hesitant at first because I’m a little worried about ordering form fitting clothes online. This dress makes me feel SO CUTE. it’s like a tshirt material with some stretch to it, super flattering and hugs the right places. I didn’t think I would like this as much as I do. My only criticism is that it is on the shorter side, I’m 5’3” and it falls above the knee. Nothing wrong with that, just shorter than I had expected. I ordered a large, I usually wear size 8-10 and it fits like a glove. The cutest little black dress with a spooky girl twist. I seriously love it.
Obsessed with this beanie, I have a big head and came fitting well and not too tight. It’s a longer style, so when it’s on there is extra room at the top as well. Going to purchase another
Would purchase again, better than expected.

Poorly printed, has lines like the printer was malfunctioning or running out of ink on the M and N. also has “worlds best boss” on the other side.
Mug is really small as well.
Bought as a Christmas gift and won’t have time to return but quality is awful.
